# Python Environment

Before running any Python code in the terminal, activate the conda environment using:

```bash
conda_ai
```

This alias sets up the correct `ai` conda environment with all required dependencies. Always run `conda_ai` before executing Python scripts, launching Jupyter, or running any Python-related commands.
